? (ASL 1, ASL 2, ASL 3, and ASL 4)  for $79.95?  \nSee \"SuperUSB\" in the ASLUniversity bookstore at: https://lifeprint.com/bookstore/books...\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see:    / billvicars  \nTo learn basic fingerspelling see    • ABC's in ASL: Learn how to Fingerspell!  \n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages...\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\nDr. Bill\n:)","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":72,"length":25,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBQQ040EGAYiEwjjs72_t-uTAxWoo4oHHTpDDNNI_PWBqJ3nr5MTygEEXUuYYA==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbTFaMDNPaS1VYnVuZXlHLWo2N1hLLWEwUkFpUXxBQ3Jtc0ttVi12LXZKX3hFbHdYOU1EaklNQ0IzMmVzYzd2cXNsU1R0aEpvbVhxUkppbjY4R1QwM2NxWTQtSlFpUV9HLWdSZkd0VGlXMFpTQ29lb2NSQU40Sy1SMFZRZkh4WTdTZ1p0NHJ4aFBDV1JsZFl0ZUZSTQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=Eya_OdUAevw","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbTFaMDNPaS1VYnVuZXlHLWo2N1hLLWEwUkFpUXxBQ3Jtc0ttVi12LXZKX3hFbHdYOU1EaklNQ0IzMmVzYzd2cXNsU1R0aEpvbVhxUkppbjY4R1QwM2NxWTQtSlFpUV9HLWdSZkd0VGlXMFpTQ29lb2NSQU40Sy1SMFZRZkh4WTdTZ1p0NHJ4aFBDV1JsZFl0ZUZSTQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=Eya_OdUAevw","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":184,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBQQ040EGAYiEwjjs72_t-uTAxWoo4oHHTpDDNNI_PWBqJ3nr5MTygEEXUuYYA==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbTJxT3FjU1dsUlFfWk5aVGQ4QmRzVHEzYmk5UXxBQ3Jtc0tsb1ZvWTlVM0tNTHAyZkhrd0E3VWdJanBEUDlsSnl5VWkwNkY2d3F4QmV4Q2xJbVBVa3U1YnEtN2otaXVPTG1KWmloNzlxT2dFNjRfNmhKSVNaUzVWNEdHUi1IVGc2UGcxWU1WbHl5a0RfYXJPd282RQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.paypal.com%2Fcgi-bin%2Fwebscr%3Fcmd%3D_s-xclick%26ho